---
title: One-Pot Shrimp and Orzo with Peas and Lemon
description: One-pot dinners to the rescue! Since everyone seems to love orzo, we thought: why not boil it with tomatoes, shrimp, and aromatics to soak up all the flavor? Sweet green peas are tossed in at the very end, but we have a feeling even the pickiest of eaters won’t be complaining about it.
